translation[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Hâ. Mîm
  44,2,Nguchilumbila Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chakusalichisya
  44,3,"Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye jalakwe (Qur’an) m’Chilo Chaupile, chisimu Uwwe tuŵele Akutetela"
  44,4,Mu chele (chilochi) chikasaŵichidwaga m’mangwakwe chindu chilichose chalunda lwakusokoka
  44,5,"Kwa ulamusi wakuuma Kukwetu, chisimu Uwwe tuŵele Ŵakutumisya (Achimitenga)"
  44,6,"Kuŵa ukoto wakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  44,7,"M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, nam’baga jenumanja n’di ŵakusimichisya (chikulupi chenu tinsimichisye yele)"
  44,8,"Pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun’galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, jukupelekaga umi ni chiwa, M’mbuje gwenu nambo soni M’mbuje jwa achatati ŵenu ŵandanda"
  44,9,"Nambo ŵanganyao (achimakafili) ali m’chikaiko, agamba ng’anda (pakuya isako yao yakusakala)"
  44,10,Basi lijembecheyani lisiku lyalichiyika liwunde ni lyosi lyakuloleka
  44,11,"Lyalichawunichila ŵandu, (ni tachiti): “Ayi ni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  44,12,"“Ambuje ŵetu! Tukungunukulilani ilagasyo, chisimu uwwe chituŵe ŵakulupilila.”"
  44,13,"(Ana lelo) kumbuchila chikwakamuchisye chichi ŵanganyao, kutendaga pamasile pajwaichilile Ntenga jwakusalichisya"
  44,14,"Kaneka ŵantundumalile ni ŵatite: “Jutekwiganyisyidwa (yalakweyi, ngaŵa yakutyochela kwa Allah, nambo soni) jwamasoka.”"
  44,15,"Chisimu Uwwe tuli tutite tunkungunukulile ilagasyo panandipe, chisimu ŵanganyammwe mpaka m’bujile (ku ukafili wenu)"
  44,16,"(Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatuchikwembekanya kwembekanya kwekulungwa (pakupeleka ipotesi kwa achimakafili), chisimu Uwwe ni ŵakuusya mbusyo (syakupoteka kusyene)"
  44,17,"Soni chisimu chene nkanayiche ŵanganyao (Makuraishi) twalinjile mayeso ŵandu ŵa Firiauna, ni jwaichilile Ntenga jwakuchimbichika (Musa)"
  44,18,"(Ni jwatite): “Mumbani achikapolo ŵa Allah (ŵanache ŵa Israila), chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”"